Retail group TFG has announced its Black Friday 2020 plans including twenty online sites, multiple brands and over 3,000 outlets. The Foschini Group (TFG), whose brands include clothing store Jet and jeweller Galaxy & Co, said it will offer deals across its brands for several weeks as part of its sale. “As we continue to adhere to Covid-19 regulations, it is important that we provide customers with choice and flexibility during the Black Friday period,” said TFG chief executive Anthony Thunström. “We have extended our Black Friday offering with the first TFG brand kicking off on 16 November and our last brand promotion ending 6 December, giving customers 21 days to shop great offers and deals this year. “Offers vary from three for two, percentage off offers, Buy one get one free, and online exclusive deals.” Some of the stores and brands which fall under the TFG include: @home
Donna
Exact
